incidents.title:
Interview with Khaled Kabbara, UNHCR GCC Spokesperson and External Relations Officer for the UAE: Dubai Humanitarian hosts one of UNHCR’s largest global stockpiles, with the capacity to support the needs of more than 700,000 people in the event of humanitarian emergencies anywhere in the world.
Thanks to the generous support and facilitation provided by the United Arab Emirates and Dubai, UNHCR continues to deliver rapid humanitarian response operations worldwide.

